title: Gabby Petito’s final days: odd texts, growing tension, severe anxiety detailed in search warrant
author: NBC2 News
description: The North Port Police Department and Sarasota County executed a search warrant on September 16 in connection to the investigation into the disappearance of Gabby Petito.
